## ```INSTALL And UNINSTALL```
> npm install xoriznapp
>  
> npm uninstall xoriznapp


## ```Pinterst```
``` 
const xapp = require('xoriznapp');
const src = 'anime'

xapp.pinterest(src)
    .then(result => {
     console.log(result)
});
```
## ```Instagram```
``` 
const xapp = require('xoriznapp');
const link = 'https://www.instagram.com/p/CVNkCZphLDI/?utm_medium=copy_link'

xapp.igdl(link)
    .then(result => {
     console.log(result)
});
```

## ```y2mate```

``` 
});

    .then(result => {
     console.log(result)
});
```
